4) Data Cleaning:
Data was checked for missing values and validated for incorrect/misspelled values.

5) Analysis:
•	Tables of name, order count, units sold and revenue of both cookie products and customers for 2020.
•	Line and clustered column chart showing the monthly revenue and count of orders for oatmeal raisin cookies for ACME Bites in 2020 (plus chocolate chip & cookies in a slicer)

6) Key Insights:
•	ACME Bites is the top customer, followed by Wholesome Foods
•	Chocolate Chip cookies generated the highest revenue, and is ordered year-round
•	2nd best-selling products are Oatmeal Raisin and white Chocolate Macadamia Nut Cookies for ACME Bites and Wholesome Foods, respectively.
•	Top-products’ sales peak mid-year for ACME bites, and in December for Chocolate chip Cookies & mid-year for White Chocolate Macadamia Nut Cookies for Wholesome Foods

